question: Show jazz bands and rock bands founded in 1985.
sql_query1:
SELECT Music_Bands.Name 
FROM Music_Bands
WHERE (Music_Bands.Genre = "Jazz" OR Music_Bands.Genre = "Rock") AND Music_Bands.Founding_Year = 1985
sql_query2:
SELECT Music_Bands.Name 
FROM Music_Bands
WHERE Music_Bands.Genre = "Jazz" OR Music_Bands.Genre = "Rock" AND Music_Bands.Founding_Year = 1985
interpretation1: What jazz bands were founded in 1985 and what rock bands were founded in the same year?
interpretation2: List all jazz bands and also list rock bands that were founded in 1985.
